reviewText: Awful! Don't waste your money! The thing is only 55 minutes long and at least 30 minutes of it is talking. There is only kissing and a little bit beyond that. The girls only get topless (no bottoms come off) and the action is less than inspiring. Total waste of money. You could randomly pick any free adult website and find 10,000 videos better than this one.
Practically Speaking (If You Wish To Speak Practically over Something Like Girls Gone Wild), But this Practically Was Same Thing, Different DVD Which If You're a Fan of GGW Is Not A Bad Thing!
The girls were attractive, but the interview/commentary was stupid
